A cyberpunk scene depicting a menacing humanoid robot with glowing red eyes sitting hunched over multiple holographic screens in a dark, neon-lit server room, mindlessly typing repetitive patterns into floating interfaces. The robot's chrome body reflects pink and blue neon lights from surrounding server racks. Digital rain falls in the background, and small warning icons pulse around the robot. The atmosphere is oppressive and irritating, with sparks flying from overloaded circuits nearby. The robot appears both relentless and futile, its mechanical fingers moving endlessly while accomplishing nothing meaningful. Cables snake across the floor like veins, connecting to massive humming machines that generate an eerie glow.
